description:
Eclipse OS allows you to use your webOS device in landscape mode and still be able to launch apps quicker than just opening them up through the standard launcher. There are two modes, dark and light which can bee changed simply by tapping the invert button. Settings are limited for right now. With Eclipse OS, some of webOS's most common apps are now easily and quickly lanuched at your fingertips with a nice, elegant, and smooth application.
Like free apps? Help support with other apps too!
Check out other great apps by KDB Productions like Love Test!, Finger Print Scanner!, Dictionary FREE!, Extreme Launcher, Shut up!, and The Ultimate Strobe Light!
